subject: Rachel Alexandra (Race Horse)
Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: The filly roared to a 10 ½-length victory in the Grade II Fleur de Lis Handicap at Churchill Downs and stayed on pace to run in the Breeders’ Cup this fall.
